WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:03.879
<i>Previously on</i>
Project Blue Book...

00:03.960 --> 00:07.158
I didn't pay much attention to the stories
till I had my first encounter.

00:07.240 --> 00:09.197
With a UFO?

00:09.320 --> 00:11.755
"Unidentified Flying Object."
Hasn't caught on yet.

00:11.840 --> 00:15.277
I don't care if we have to drop a nuke
to take Fuller out.

00:15.360 --> 00:17.352
There's a lot of people
looking for you.

00:17.440 --> 00:19.955
There is where it all started.
It's the program.

00:20.080 --> 00:22.016
- Do you want to tell me about that?
- We get messages.

00:22.040 --> 00:23.040
<i>We're the antennas.</i>

00:23.120 --> 00:24.839
I keep seeing this.

00:24.960 --> 00:27.111
I'm sorry.

00:27.200 --> 00:28.200
No! Stop!

00:29.200 --> 00:32.192
<i>When you see someone die,
it's tempting to want to blame yourself.</i>

